WEBVTT

00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:16.400
<i>Who is he?</i>

00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:20.190
<i>She's Jolyne Cujoh!</i>

00:00:20.280 --> 00:00:22.320
<i>Not Lang Rangler!</i>

00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:27.120
<i>Should I assume that he failed,</i>
<i>and she's the one with the disc?</i>

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:31.950
<i>In a matter of minutes,</i> <i>her ally will come</i>
<i>and get the disc at the courtyard.</i>

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:36.040
He's the chaplain of this prison.

00:00:36.830 --> 00:00:38.170
Why is he here now?

00:00:38.670 --> 00:00:40.130
<i>She knows who I am.</i>

00:00:41.050 --> 00:00:46.140
<i>No, she would've already attacked me</i>
<i>if she knew I was her enemy.</i>

00:00:46.220 --> 00:00:48.140
Wait! Please, Father!

00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:49.850
Please…

00:00:49.930 --> 00:00:51.970
Don't sound the alarm!

00:00:52.060 --> 00:00:55.350
I'm not here to cause any trouble!

00:00:56.060 --> 00:00:57.020
<i>What should I do?</i>

00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:59.190
<i>It would be easy to beat him unconscious.</i>

00:00:59.270 --> 00:01:02.480
<i>That's nothing</i>
<i>compared to my father's life.</i>

00:01:03.070 --> 00:01:04.320
<i>Hitting him is nothing…</i>

00:01:06.700 --> 00:01:08.990
There is already a problem.

00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:13.500
You unlocked the door
using another inmate's work permit.

00:01:14.500 --> 00:01:19.790
Where is the owner of this permit,
the inmate, Lang Rangler?

00:01:20.460 --> 00:01:24.630
I know I just met you,
and I don't expect you to believe me.

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.590
But I'm no liar, Father.

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:29.220
That inmate attacked me.

00:01:29.850 --> 00:01:31.100
It was self-defense.

00:01:31.720 --> 00:01:35.060
He's passed out in that basket over there.

00:01:35.140 --> 00:01:39.270
I must report this to the authorities.

00:01:39.860 --> 00:01:41.690
I understand, Father.

00:01:41.770 --> 00:01:44.650
But it has to be
after I go to the courtyard.

00:01:44.740 --> 00:01:46.240
I only need two minutes…

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.860
No, give me just a single minute, Father.

00:01:48.950 --> 00:01:52.240
I must go to the courtyard.
That's all I ask.

00:01:53.950 --> 00:01:56.620
You want me to turn a blind eye?

00:01:57.250 --> 00:01:58.960
It's a matter of life and death.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:01.960
My father's life and soul depend on it.

00:02:02.460 --> 00:02:05.380
A man of God should understand.

00:02:05.460 --> 00:02:07.170
Are you here by yourself?

00:02:07.800 --> 00:02:10.090
Is there anyone else with you?

00:02:11.050 --> 00:02:13.060
No, I'm alone.

00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:16.180
<i>I lied to a chaplain.</i>

00:02:16.270 --> 00:02:19.270
<i>But surely, a small lie can be forgiven.</i>

00:02:19.350 --> 00:02:22.020
<i>And I can't tell him about the disc.</i>

00:02:22.610 --> 00:02:23.820
Please.

00:02:23.900 --> 00:02:25.650
I only need a minute.

00:02:25.730 --> 00:02:32.530
Doing something for others
is all an act of expecting a reward.

00:02:32.620 --> 00:02:37.290
To be kind to others
is to be kind to oneself.

00:02:37.370 --> 00:02:39.500
There is no such thing as
unconditional love.

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:41.710
Because unconditional love

00:02:42.630 --> 00:02:45.210
is a reward to go to heaven.

00:02:46.050 --> 00:02:47.460
You may go.

00:02:47.550 --> 00:02:49.760
I will pretend I didn't see you here.

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:54.470
But only a minute as requested.

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:57.640
You have to come back
to this gate by then.

00:03:02.480 --> 00:03:03.690
<i>I have no choice.</i>

00:03:04.230 --> 00:03:06.820
<i>Someone is hiding behind that container.</i>

00:03:07.440 --> 00:03:08.900
<i>If she has an ally with her,</i>

00:03:08.990 --> 00:03:10.650
<i>I can't reveal myself.</i>

00:03:10.740 --> 00:03:14.780
<i>I can't expose Whitesnake and kill Jolyne.</i>

