That is what you're thinking, right?

00:16:08.390 --> 00:16:12.600
Then come towards my voice.

00:16:17.520 --> 00:16:20.740
Father!

00:16:21.650 --> 00:16:24.740
Jotaro Kujo's disc, Star Platinum.

00:16:25.700 --> 00:16:27.660
What should I do with it?

00:16:27.740 --> 00:16:30.830
I have eliminated Jolyne Cujoh,
but I cannot leave her there.

00:16:31.410 --> 00:16:33.580
Did the gate open?

00:16:33.670 --> 00:16:35.170
Take me with you…

00:16:35.250 --> 00:16:36.080
Father?

00:16:36.670 --> 00:16:39.800
Where are you, Father?!

00:16:41.010 --> 00:16:42.800
<i>I'm at the end of my rope.</i>

00:16:43.380 --> 00:16:45.090
<i>I can't guard against the the poison!</i>

00:16:45.180 --> 00:16:47.050
<i>The disc that I let go…</i>

00:16:47.640 --> 00:16:49.390
<i>I don't know where it is anymore!</i>

00:17:05.660 --> 00:17:07.120
The rain stopped.

00:17:08.780 --> 00:17:12.700
Where is Jolyne Cujoh's corpse?

00:17:13.450 --> 00:17:16.540
The disc must be close by.

00:17:17.130 --> 00:17:18.960
<i>That was vexing,</i>

00:17:19.040 --> 00:17:21.920
<i>but my Snake would never lose to frogs.</i>

00:17:22.590 --> 00:17:24.010
<i>Search for it.</i>

00:17:24.670 --> 00:17:28.260
<i>Whitesnake's range is 20 meters at most.</i>

00:17:28.340 --> 00:17:32.850
<i>It would pose a serious problem</i>
<i>if anyone spots me here,</i>

00:17:33.560 --> 00:17:35.310
<i>but I'm out of options.</i>

00:17:39.230 --> 00:17:41.860
The soul of a dead criminal

00:17:41.940 --> 00:17:47.200
returns to the earth in the form of a frog
in want of companions to the afterlife.

00:17:47.280 --> 00:17:50.620
I've heard of such a legend
existing in the East.

00:17:50.700 --> 00:17:54.450
Doesn't it describe
this hellish scene perfectly?

00:17:54.540 --> 00:17:57.920
And the disc must be
somewhere around here.

00:17:59.040 --> 00:17:59.960
Whitesnake.

00:18:00.920 --> 00:18:04.300
Search towards the gate from there.

00:18:05.010 --> 00:18:07.260
The guard might have taken it.

00:18:07.340 --> 00:18:09.430
It must be within that direction.

00:18:11.470 --> 00:18:12.510
I found it!

00:18:15.680 --> 00:18:17.600
I've recovered the disc.

00:18:18.440 --> 00:18:19.480
Thanks.

00:18:19.560 --> 00:18:22.070
I was waiting for you to find it.

