00:20:03.960 --> 00:20:09.260
He won't even recall his own daughter!

00:20:09.340 --> 00:20:11.920
Look! A guard is down!

00:20:12.010 --> 00:20:13.430
Don't step on the frogs!

00:20:13.510 --> 00:20:15.220
Search the courtyard!

00:20:15.300 --> 00:20:16.720
Someone might be there!

00:20:19.720 --> 00:20:22.520
<i>Don't blank out yet.</i>

00:20:22.600 --> 00:20:24.730
<i>Its Stand User must be close by.</i>

00:20:25.980 --> 00:20:29.150
<i>I must find Whitesnake's Stand User first.</i>

00:20:29.230 --> 00:20:32.990
<i>The User has my father's memory disc.</i>

00:20:33.070 --> 00:20:36.450
<i>Now's my chance to find its User!</i>

00:20:37.990 --> 00:20:40.410
Hey! Look out the window!

00:20:40.490 --> 00:20:41.370
Oh my god!

00:20:41.450 --> 00:20:43.790
It's a miracle! It has to be!

00:20:44.540 --> 00:20:46.290
But who's going to clean this up?

00:20:46.790 --> 00:20:48.460
<i>The tide hasn't changed.</i>

00:20:49.050 --> 00:20:51.800
<i>I took Jotaro's Star Platinum</i>

00:20:51.880 --> 00:20:55.930
<i>only out of my pledge</i>
<i>to avenge Dio, my friend.</i>

00:20:56.640 --> 00:20:59.390
<i>The memory disc is the one that matters,</i>

00:20:59.470 --> 00:21:01.390
<i>and it's in my hands.</i>

00:21:01.470 --> 00:21:03.520
<i>Everything is according to plan.</i>

00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:05.560
<i>Only Jotaro's memory</i>

00:21:05.650 --> 00:21:08.060
<i>contains clues to attain heaven.</i>

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:22.580
<i>An abnormal situation where frogs</i>
<i>rain only in the prison courtyard.</i>

00:21:26.170 --> 00:21:31.420
<i>Jolyne's escape attempt</i>
<i>was unquestioned in this chaos.</i>

00:21:34.970 --> 00:21:41.640
<i>And The Speedwagon Foundation</i>
<i>obtained Jotaro Kujo's Star Platinum disc.</i>

00:21:42.220 --> 00:21:48.020
<i>But Jotaro's soul won't return</i>
<i>without the Memory disc.</i>

00:22:00.020 --> 00:22:05.020
Although you think I cope

00:22:05.020 --> 00:22:10.020
My head is filled with hope

00:22:10.020 --> 00:22:18.970
Of some place other than here

00:22:20.370 --> 00:22:25.020
Although you think I smile

00:22:25.020 --> 00:22:30.220
Inside and all the while

00:22:30.220 --> 00:22:39.020
I'm wondering about my destiny

00:22:39.020 --> 00:22:45.370
I'm thinking about

00:22:45.370 --> 00:22:50.120
All the things

00:22:50.120 --> 00:22:54.920
I'd like to do

00:22:54.920 --> 00:22:59.670
In my life

00:22:59.670 --> 00:23:04.420
I'm a dreamer

00:23:04.420 --> 00:23:09.320
A distant dreamer

00:23:09.320 --> 00:23:15.120
Dreaming far away

00:23:15.120 --> 00:23:18.770
From today

00:23:22.620 --> 00:23:24.030
Sports Maximum.

00:23:24.620 --> 00:23:27.410
I wanted to ask you about this bone.

00:23:28.080 --> 00:23:32.210
I want you to try something
using your ability.

00:23:32.790 --> 00:23:35.500
Is that a human bone?

00:23:35.590 --> 00:23:36.800
Whose is it?

00:23:36.880 --> 00:23:38.710
That doesn't concern you.

00:23:38.800 --> 00:23:41.430
Let's just say it belongs to
an old friend of mine.

00:23:42.470 --> 00:23:44.050
<i>My dear friend,</i>

00:23:44.140 --> 00:23:46.060
<i>Dio's bone.</i>